{"tid":1527152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共政法委：不要幻想蒙面就能躲得過、逃得脫","createTime":"2019-09-01T09:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:14:51.000Z","uid":216992,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0d78420741b4068ae6ef4f9a314915aea88c820c","tid":1527152,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:11:54.000Z","msg":"中共政法委指港示威者躲不過十五<br />\n<br />\n中央政法委發文，指犯下暴行的香港示威者，不要幻想蒙面就能躲得過、逃得脫。 <br />\n<br />\n中央政法委凌晨在微信公眾號「中央政法委長安劍」發文，指示威者的暴行，早已遠遠脫離遊行及示威的範疇，而是採取恐怖主義手法，又稱美國國旗在示威中招搖過市、耀武揚威，受外部勢力干預的跡象「一覽無餘」，又形容「躲得過初一，躲不過十五」，離月圓之夜還有幾天，叫暴徒自己數手指算一算。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣的中央社報道認為，文章暗示九月十三日中秋節，有擴大執法行動的可能性。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556228/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%94%BF%E6%B3%95%E5%A7%94%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%BA%B2%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556228%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25BA%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25BA%2594&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b926ad5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556228%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25BA%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25BA%2594&h=3795e88d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556228/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%94%BF%E6%B3%95%E5%A7%94%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%